articles.author: Brooks Barnes
articles.title: 'Top Gun: Maverick' Lands Triumphantly on Opening Weekend - The New York Times
articles.description: The film industry takes the estimated $151 million in North American ticket sales as a breakthrough after a long pandemic slump.
articles.content: Euphoric reviews and strong word of mouth helped boost ticket sales, which easily surpassed prerelease analyst expectations. Top Gun: Maverick received a rare A-plus grade from ticket buyers in Cinem… [+2375 chars]
